  "body": "🚨🚨🚨 **HOW TO GET THIS UPDATE (v3.05)** 🚨🚨🚨\n\nAlways use the same download link from your original Gumroad email. Open that email and click the same link — it will automatically download the latest version (3.05).\n\n→ You NEVER need to purchase again to receive updates.\n\n## 🎉 Stable Release 3.05\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### ✨ New Features\n\n- **Conditional Math Logic Wizard:**\n  - Build complex interactive logic with zero code.\n  - Evaluate a widget’s value and perform math operations on a persistent variable.\n  - Perfect for counters, score systems, dynamic calculations, and state-based interactions.\n\n- **Array / List Manager (In-Memory):**\n  - Create and manage arrays/lists stored in memory.\n  - Add, remove, update, and retrieve values dynamically.\n  - Designed for advanced state management without writing code.\n\n### 📂 New Demo Included\n\n- **demo_new_logic_command.json:** Demonstrates both the Conditional Math wizard and the Array/List Manager in action.\n\n---\n\n🚨🚨🚨 **HOW TO GET THIS UPDATE (v3.04)** 🚨🚨🚨\n\nAlways use the same download link from your original Gumroad email. Open that email and click the same link — it will automatically download the latest version (3.04).\n\n→ You NEVER need to purchase again to receive updates.\n\n## 🎉 Stable Release 3.04\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### 🎬 New FFmpeg Plugin\n\n- **Brand new FFmpeg plugin included.**\n- **26 built-in FFmpeg commands available.**\n\n### 🧩 Improvements\n\n- **Added new Wizard commands.**\n- **Bugs fixed.**\n- **New demos added.**\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 3.03\n\n## 🎉 Stable Release 3.03\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### 🎬 FFmpeg Multimedia Updates\n\n- **New multimedia commands for FFmpeg.**\n- **New demo project:** demo_ffmpeg_editor.json\n- **Minor bugs fixed.**\n\n### 🧩 Property Panel — New Enhancements\n\n#### Fixed Controls (Always Visible in Appearance Section)\n\n- **Enabled:** Toggle to set the widget’s initial enabled/disabled state.\n- **Opacity:** 0–100% spinbox using real QGraphicsOpacityEffect.\n- **Tooltip:** Help text displayed on hover.\n\n#### Improved Text & Font Section\n\n- **Bold / Italic:** Quick toggle checkboxes (no font dialog needed).\n- **Font Size:** Direct size spinbox in the panel.\n- **Letter Spacing:** Character spacing in pixels.\n- **Alignment:** Now supported for Button, Label, Input, TextArea, CheckBox, and RadioButton.\n- **Word Wrap:** Available for Label and TextArea.\n\n#### Widget-Specific Properties\n\n- **Input Fields:** Placeholder text, Read Only, Password Mode, Max Length.\n- **Button:** Checkable (toggle), Initially Checked, Flat style.\n- **Label:** Open External Links.\n- **CheckBox / RadioButton:** Initially Checked.\n- **Timer:** Interval (ms), Single Shot.\n- **ProgressBar:** Show % Text, Custom Format (%p%, %v/%m).\n- **Slider:** Tick Marks (position), Tick Interval.\n- **ComboBox:** Editable mode.\n- **ListBox:** Multi-select.\n- **TableWidget:** Show Grid, Sortable.\n- **TextArea:** Tab Width (characters).\n- **SpinBox / DoubleSpinBox:** Wrap Around.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 3.00\n\n## 🎉 Stable Release 3.00\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### 🧩 Editor Improvements\n\n- **Select All Widgets (Page Option):** New option to quickly select all widgets on the current page for faster editing and bulk operations.\n\n### 🖥 System Tray Support\n\n- **System Tray Icon Demo:** Added a new demo project showcasing how to use the system tray icon functionality in desktop applications.\n\n### 🎨 Style Manager Enhancements\n\n- **More Built-in Themes:** Added additional themes to the Style Manager plugin for improved UI customization.\n\n### 🪟 New Plugin: Dialog Builder\n\n- **Dialog Builder Plugin:** New visual tool to easily create and manage custom dialogs.\n- **Dialog Builder Demo:** Included a dedicated demo project demonstrating how to build and use dialogs.\n\n### 🛠 Smarter Error Detection\n\n- **Improved Intelligent Error Detection:** Enhanced detection for common mistakes in Global Code and widget events.\n- The system now attempts to predict frequent errors and provide clearer, more helpful feedback directly to the user.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.99\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.99\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### 🛠 Improved Error Reporting (F5 Preview)\n\n- **Runtime Errors Improved:** Runtime errors in F5 Preview now show the exact line in your code (Global Code or widget event) instead of a raw _f5_preview.py line number.\n- **Canvas Configuration Errors:** Errors such as wrong widget type or incompatible initial values are now clearly identified by widget ID, including a direct hint to fix them directly in the canvas.\n\n### 📊 Table Widget Improvements\n\n- **10 New Commands for Table Widget:** Expanded functionality with ten new built-in commands to provide more control and flexibility when working with tables.\n- **New Table Widget Demo:** Added a dedicated demo project showcasing the new Table Widget capabilities.\n- **New Demo:** demo_demo_dashboard.json – Example dashboard project demonstrating advanced layout and table integration.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.98\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.98\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n### ✨ New Widgets\n\n- **DraggableTableWidget:** Editable drag-and-drop table  \n  - Configurable rows and columns with customizable headers.  \n  - Wizard commands: set_cell, get_cell, load_csv, get_selected_row.\n\n- **DraggableFileDropZone:** File drag-and-drop area  \n  - Drop a file onto the widget to capture its path.  \n  - on_file_dropped event available in preview.\n\n### ✨ New Wizard Commands\n\n- **Table Widget:** Set Cell, Get Cell, Load CSV, Get Selected Row  \n- **File Operations:** Read File, Write File, Open Dialog, Save Dialog  \n\n## 📂 New Demos Included\n\n- **demo_table_csv.json:** Table that loads CSV files, edits cells, and saves changes.  \n- **demo_file_manager.json:** File manager example using FileDropZone with file reading and writing support.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.97\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.97\n\n## ✨ New Features & Wizards\n\n- **Data Binding & Sync:** Added Bind Value to automatically sync text/values between widgets (e.g., SpinBox → Label).\n- **No-Code Logic:** Added Checkbox Controller (Show/Hide/Enable targets based on state) and Value Router (trigger actions based on specific values).\n- **Data Persistence (INI):** Added Save/Load Setting and Batch Form Processing (Save/Load Form) to easily store user data in local settings.ini files.\n- **System Utilities:** Added commands to Open URL, Open Local Folder, Get Date/Time, and Copy to Clipboard.\n- **Geometry & Layout:** Added Center Widget (auto-centering), Move Relative (offset/nudge), and Get Geometry (read X, Y, W, H into variables).\n- **3D Support:** New 3D OpenGL Viewer plugin and demo.\n\n## 📂 New Demos Included\n\n- **demo_widgets_events.json:** Interactive showcase of CheckBox, ComboBox, ListBox, and SpinBox events.\n- **demo_widgets_events_wizard.json:** Demonstrates the new Sync, Checkbox Controller, and Router wizards without writing code.\n- **demo_commands_ini.json:** Shows how to save preferences to .ini, use AutoRun, and System Utilities (Time/Open Folder).\n- **demo_save_load_ini_batch.json:** A complete User Profile example using Batch Save/Load for multiple fields at once.\n- **demo_geometry_commands.json:** Interactive playground for Get Info, Auto-Center, and Relative Movement controls.\n- **demo_3d_opengl.json:** Showcase of the new 3D OpenGL Viewer plugin.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.96\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.96\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n- **Fixed:** Cursor style issues in Image elements.\n- **New:** Added new anchor positions for centered layouts.\n- **New Demo:** Anchor positioning demo project.\n- **New Demo:** Simple Visual Novel example project.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.95\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.95\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n- **New:** Project Settings option to include the entire assets folder (no smart scan).\n- **New:** Build option for CLI-only (Command Line Interface) applications.\n- **Core Update:** Modified engine to properly support console-only CLI applications.\n- **New:** CMD button in the Console/Debug toolbar to open the original system console and interact with CLI applications directly.\n- **New Examples:** \"Simple CLI\" demo project.\n- **New Examples:** Advanced CLI demo using Textual (TUI-based interface).\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.94\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.94\n\n## ✨ What's New\n\n- **AI Optimization:** Only current page context, global code, and page names are sent.\n- **Fixed:** F5 preview now correctly uses project directory; relative paths work.\n- **PDF Maker:** Containers supported for PDF export (no images).\n- **New:** Light obfuscation for user variables.\n- **UI:** Resizable projects enforce minimum window size.\n\n---\n\n### Previous Version — 2.93\n\n## 🎉 Stable Early Access Release 2.93\n\n## ✨ Highlights\n\n- **New demos:** CSV Editor, Memory Game, File Save demo, Simon Game.\n- **Export:** Added macOS and Linux options.\n- **Bug Fix:** Syntax error in comment-only code blocks fixed.\n- **Security:** AI API Keys encrypted in config.\n- **Build:** Dialog to manage Hidden Imports and debug options.\n- **Performance:** Undo/Redo memory optimized (20 steps).\n- **Localization:** Updated translations.\"\n}\n
